allocPSA Installation
=====================

allocPSA is intended to run with PHP and MySQL on a Linux server.  If you
manage to get it running on an alternate operating system then please let us
know about it.


1) Put the source code in a directory called eg "alloc" in your webservers
   document root.

2) Open that URL with your web browser eg: http://webserver/alloc/
   and complete the installation.


Please feel free to contact us at Cybersource <info@cyber.com.au> or just use the 
forums at http://sourceforge.net/projects/allocpsa/ if you have any questions.


